title: Artificial intelligence isn't 'necessary for anything', says Musk
description: Elon Musk has hit out at artificial intelligence (AI), saying it is not "necessary for anything we're doing".

title: Netflix reminds password sharers of the rules as crackdown continues
description: Netflix has expanded its crackdown on password sharing, reminding those breaking the rules worldwide their accounts cannot be accessed for free outside their households.

title: Student 'caused fatal school dormitory fire because her phone was confiscated'
description: A fire which killed 19 people at a secondary school dormitory in Guyana was deliberately set by a student, according to an official.

title: 'Contempt is punishable': Trump warned by judge after appearing virtually in court over hush money case
description: Donald Trump has appeared in court via video link to receive a warning from a judge over evidence sharing in his criminal hush money case.

title: £1.8bn aid package announced for flood-hit areas in northern Italy
description: Italy has announced a £1.8bn (€2bn) package to help the flood-stricken areas of northern Italy after thousands of people were forced from their homes due to the destruction.

title: Man killed by car after stopping to help family of ducks cross busy road
description: A "kind and amazing" father-of-two has been struck and killed by a car after he got out of his own vehicle to help a family of ducks cross a busy intersection in California.

title: Did pro-Ukrainian fighters capture a Russian town?
description: There is still widespread confusion over reports of an armed raid across the Ukrainian border into Russia, with claims of pro-Ukrainian fighters capturing a town and the use of a tank.

title: Man scales Mount Everest for a record 28th time
description: A veteran Sherpa guide has scaled Mount Everest for the 28th time, beating his own record.

title: New Zealand's ratio of sheep to people falls to record low
description: New Zealand's ratio of sheep to humans has dropped below five to one - the lowest ever recorded.

title: Who is Christian B - the main suspect in the Madeleine McCann case?
description: Investigators are searching a reservoir in the Algarve allegedly frequented by the main suspect in the Madeleine McCann case.

title: Truck crashes into barriers near White House as driver arrested
description: A truck driver has been arrested after crashing into security barriers near the White House.

title: Hippos and killer whales among five more species to be added to ivory ban list
description: Trading ivory from a hippo, walrus, narwhal, killer whale and sperm whale will soon be illegal, the government says.
